---
// 並列化戦略 — メインチャットとforkの役割分担
---

<figure class="parallel" aria-label="並列化戦略：メインチャットとforkの役割分担">
  <div class="parallel__inner">
    <span class="parallel__title-label">並列化戦略</span>

    <div class="parallel__diagram">
      <!-- Main chat -->
      <div class="parallel__node parallel__node--main">
        <span class="parallel__node-name">メインチャット</span>
        <span class="parallel__node-role">コード変更に集中</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Fork branch -->
      <div class="parallel__branch" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="parallel__branch-line">
          <div class="parallel__branch-vert"></div>
          <div class="parallel__branch-horiz"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="parallel__fork-row">
        <div class="parallel__fork-label">
          <code class="parallel__fork-cmd">/fork</code>
        </div>
        <div class="parallel__node parallel__node--fork">
          <span class="parallel__node-name">サブチャット</span>
          <span class="parallel__node-role">調査・リサーチ・ドキュメント参照</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parallel__rule">
      <span class="parallel__rule-label">原則</span>
      <span class="parallel__rule-text">最小限の並列化で最大の成果。同時に抱えるタスクは 3〜4 つまで。</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="parallel__caption">
    複数インスタンスが同じコードベースを触る場合は Git Worktrees でコンフリクトを防ぐ。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .parallel {
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, white),
      var(--surface)
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .parallel__inner {
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .parallel__title-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .parallel__diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 28rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Nodes */
  .parallel__node {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--bg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .parallel__node--main {
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  .parallel__node--fork {
    flex: 1;
    border-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 30%, var(--border));
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 40%, var(--bg));
  }

  .parallel__node-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .parallel__node-role {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Branch lines */
  .parallel__branch {
    padding-inline-start: 1.2rem;
    height: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .parallel__branch-line {
    position: absolute;
    inset-block-start: 0;
    inset-inline-start: 1.2rem;
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .parallel__branch-vert {
    width: 1px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--border-strong);
    margin-inline-start: 0;
  }

  /* Fork row */
  .parallel__fork-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-inline-start: 1.2rem;
  }

  .parallel__fork-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;

    &::before {
      content: "";
      display: block;
      width: 0.9rem;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border-strong);
    }
  }

  .parallel__fork-cmd {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 60%, var(--bg));
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 25%, transparent);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Rule box */
  .parallel__rule {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--bg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .parallel__rule-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .parallel__rule-text {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .parallel__caption {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-block-start: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .parallel__inner {
      padding: 1.25rem 1rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
